				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-6-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-gi%C3%A1m-v%C5%A9-c%C3%B4ng-T%C3%B4-c%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-Minh/poem-qLBRT9lcYItg15RQsy0FNQ">Bát ai thi kỳ 6 - Thiếu giám vũ công Tô công Nguyên Minh - 八哀詩其六－故秘書少監武功蘇公源明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-V%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%B1-T%C3%A1n-c%C3%B4ng-ph%C3%B2ng-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-6E5jkoKhZiYxHDfeQ-PZvg">Đại Vân tự Tán công phòng kỳ 4 - 大雲寺贊公房其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ch%E1%BA%BF-Ngh%C4%A9a/Ng%C3%B4n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-Mh6EZSjvgPq1sxjFKAV72A">Ngôn hoài - 言懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ch%E1%BA%BF-Ngh%C4%A9a/author-bF2hymwy-OyotYa-NKGX3w">Nguyễn Chế Nghĩa</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-K%E1%BB%B7/Ng%E1%BB%A5-c%C6%B0-Ng%C3%B4-H%C6%B0ng/poem-hgnlEy3g1ZrQeSQ_qIlN0g">Ngụ cư Ngô Hưng - 寓居吳興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-K%E1%BB%B7/author-rrGRphgHzx_THgdF6hbcZQ">Tăng Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-Kh%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BB%99i-ch%C3%BAng/poem-YNfeghBCLmBTPmmoWLpuIA">Nhất nhật hội chúng - 一日會眾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-Kh%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-6oFTHDWILtiNI8RyEOgPCQ">Tịnh Không thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Qu%C3%A1ch-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa-ki%C3%AAm-th%C3%A1i-b%E1%BB%99c-khanh-sung-L%C5%A9ng-H%E1%BB%AFu-ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-s%E1%BB%A9-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-2XGzR8ArLA_7rTigSktnjQ">Phụng tặng Quách trung thừa kiêm thái bộc khanh sung Lũng Hữu tiết độ sứ tam thập vận - 奉送郭中丞兼太僕卿充隴右節度使三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%A2y-K%E1%BB%B3-th%C3%B4n-t%E1%BA%A7m-tr%C3%AD-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba-d%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%BAc-T%C3%A1n-c%C3%B4ng-th%E1%BB%95-th%E1%BA%A5t-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-VfOGW3b8swUJfNF0k3kHzg">Tây Kỳ thôn tầm trí thảo đường địa, dạ túc Tán công thổ thất kỳ 1 - 西枝村尋置草堂地，夜宿贊公土室其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B7-Qu%C3%A2n/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-thu-s%C6%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-di%E1%BB%83u-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-8PEmLExOCL0amlWapI69Nw">Tự đề thu sơn độc diểu đồ - 自題秋山獨眺圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B7-Qu%C3%A2n/author-qre_2HqJKAT7IbljC2mp1w">Kỷ Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ch%C3%AD-Trung-S%C6%A1n/poem-tpTjzvRJ7pZVSIyJ7x9f5Q">Tương chí Trung Sơn - 將至中山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-vNqjO3qn_lddcLSXVQdpGA">Bồ Đạo Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/Xu%C3%A2n-d%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BA%ABu-ng%C3%A2m/poem-Oy_sgIaHh0UmXSZHe2N0Dw">Xuân dạ ngẫu ngâm - 春夜偶吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br></div>	</div>
